+  // shims). Once startup has created the expected Browser instances or other
+  // ScopedKeepAlive instances, -resetKeepAliveWhileHidden can reset
+  // `_keepAlive`.
   //
   // When the user explicitly launches Chrome, or when Chrome creates any
   // windows, the `activationPolicy` is changed by the OS. By observing
